item.title: The Hundred-Page Machine Learning Book by Andriy Burkov
item.description: Starting in the Fall semester of 2019, I will be taking a course at Carleton University on machine learning. The course description revealed that we will be working through ‘The Hundred-Page Machine Learning Book’ by Andriy Burkov. Seeing this, I decided to get a head start and go through as much of the book as I can on my own. I feel like this will be a great opportunity to learn about and implement a topic I’ve been very interested in since I heard about it.
